						               													<description>Here is your free introduction to All Units Engage!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All Units Engage is a set of simple rules for skirmish games for two or more players. Play can be based around a handful of minis or include multiple squads. &amp;#10;The game plays equally well with 15mm or 28mm miniatures.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All Units Engage is a solid &amp;ldquo;old school&amp;rdquo; game with a modern perspective. It is a game that flows very well from turn-to-turn and player to player. &amp;#10;Games are intended to be short, with an emphasis on achieving objectives inside of a brief span of turns.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All Units Engage is a toolkit that invites you to play with the minis and models you already own. &amp;#10;The focus is on sci-fi, near-future and post-apocalyptic gaming, but the mechanics are flexible enough to support a wider variety of settings such as Cold War and even WWII.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All Units Engages uses ten-sided dice. &amp;#10;No templates are required and only a few basic markers are needed to track pins and reserve actions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All Units Engage is casual, but complete. This introduction is only a taste of what AUE has to offer.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
